AnotherWar FPS Game
FPShooter Game Open Source Python Pygame
Take it from voxel sandbox graphics to better fan voted on update packages.
DOWNLOAD :::
wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/anotherwar/files/latest/download/AnotherWar.zip

# glos Great Linux Operating Sysytem
Download glos-source
https://github.com/gizmolinuxos/glos/blob/master/glos-source.zip
Download glos-addons
https://sourceforge.net/projects/gizmolinuxos/files/addon_toolbox.tar.xz/download
Extract source and addons.
Open a terminal and execute 

./0-glos.sh

Run resulting .iso in virtualbox or other vm.
